$interpreted: : One month later...
Yang-Tai's Friend: Here's everything you ordered, please make a count of it.
Yang-Tai: Thanks, old friend. Would you see to the remaining balance for us, Baa Baa?
Baa Baa: Okay~~~
Yang-Tai's Friend: ...Yang-Tai... You're not going to check through the order...?
Yang-Tai: How many times have we worked together now? I trust you completely. And even if you did make off with our money, I know exactly where you'd run to!
Yang-Tai's Friend: Uh...
Baa Baa: ……
Yang-Tai's Friend: Well... That's settled then. I have more business to see to, please don't worry about seeing me off.
Yang-Tai: Very well, take care.
Yang-Tai: Take these goods to the storehouse.
Astonished Employee: What the?! Mr. President! It's all ruined!
Yang-Tai: Let me see!
Yang-Tai: What's happened here?! It's all spoiled...
Astonished Employee: This case, too!
Baa Baa: Same here!
Yang-Tai: Check them all! Inspect every last one!
Astonished Employee: Mr. President... We've looked over every single one... Except for the case on top, all the others underneath are spoiled.
Baa Baa: ...Could he have planned to cheat us from the very beginning?
Yang-Tai: He would never... There must be some mistake...
Yang-Tai: Baa Baa, go run and bring him back! Quickly!
Baa Baa: Yes, sir!
Baa Baa: Hmm, I thought we were supposed to meet here...
Baa Baa: Hyah... What did I ever do to deserve being nipped at day after day...
???: Who wouldn't want a bite of such a naughty little lamb?
Baa Baa: What the... Ya spooked me there, don't creep up on a sheep like that.
Sennosuke: Hmph. You've done well, Baa Baa.
Baa Baa: Please, it was nothing.
Sennosuke: Without your persuasion, he'd never have agreed to this business, and then I wouldnt have had the opportunity to set the trap.
Sennosuke: After two years together, that old git was never going to suspect you. It's just the opportunity I've been looking out for after planting you by his side.
Sennosuke: Now that I've bought out the entire food supply, it's time to make a killing out of him.
Baa Baa: I thought the plan would be ruined after I heard he had his own connections.
Sennosuke: Luckily you were smart enough to take the lead in going after that friend of his.
Sennosuke: And what a fine coincidence, that his old pal happens to be an old accomplice of mine, too. That gave us just the leverage we needed.
Sennosuke: Hahaha, he never had a chance!
Baa Baa: So, is my work here all done now?
Sennosuke: No, not just yet...
